{"tid":2212683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女童母親可向投訴警察課投訴","createTime":"2020-09-22T04:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T06:28:14.000Z","uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8e171bb524dc9d64e094a91981bd5d5bb3588dd4","tid":2212683,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201506/61e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201506%2F61e0.png&h=0b24ad56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人性？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名13歲患有輕度智障之女童，去年11月遭母親遺棄於茶餐廳3小時，其35歲母被控一項對所看管兒童拋棄罪，案件今日（6月2日）在觀塘裁判法院審訊時，竟揭發警方得知女童在驗傷後證明沒有表面傷勢後，仍替她拍下4張上半身赤裸之照片，<strong><span class=\"red\">其中一張為正面半祼照</span></strong>。  <br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果日報》報道，女童母親指雖然照片是由女警拍攝，但不知相片有多少人看過，而且本案的控辯雙方代表均為男性，故要求裁判官下令警方將相片及底片銷毀。  <br />\n<br />\n控方在回應時指，拍照屬警方內部做法，也未能確定相片是在女童驗傷前或後拍攝，而且相片沒有呈堂，故此屬警方內部的事。而裁判官則要求警方將有關相片及檔案銷毀，並指<strong><span class=\"red\">女童母親可向投訴警察課投訴</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-02-2015/23383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-02-2015%2F23383&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEeu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=aa3812ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-02-2015/23383</a>"},{"pid":"565e0100ae75b0192fc5ddd7551d6a1ad08f0dda","tid":2212683,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:10:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"984e596f30267e34